    <item>
      <title>《吸血鬼猎人巴菲》中深受喜爱的配角尼古拉斯·布伦登去世，享年 54 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/arts/television/nicholas-brendon-dead.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他在一部讲述一名少女保护世界免受怪物侵害的热门电视节目中扮演巴菲最亲密的朋友之一桑德·哈里斯（Xander Harris）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/20/arts/television/nicholas-brendon-dead.html</guid>
